Source: pg-when
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), cargo, clang
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/frectonz/pg-when

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-when
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-when
Depends: postgresql-PGVERSION, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Natural-language time parsing for PostgreSQL
 pg_when turns human-readable date and time expressions into PostgreSQL
 timestamptz and epoch-based values. This package builds the pgrx-based
 extension for PostgreSQL 14 through 18 using cargo-pgrx 0.17.0.
